title: First State National Historical Park: Do Business With Us
body: Explore This Park    Get Involved     Do Business With Us             Do Business With Us       Leasing of Park Facilities   The National Park Service at First State National Historical Park is currently has multiple properties available for lease for commercial, residential, and agricultural purposes. We are looking for parties interested in these opportunity. Carefully review the Request for Proposals (RFP) for more information and deadlines on the pages below:   Current Leasing Opportunities
